summary: This document is a police summons issued for a parking violation involving Ghislaine Maxwell. The report details the violation, including the location, vehicle information, and the issuing precinct.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell

events.title: Parking Violation Summons Issued
events.description: A parking summons was issued to Ghislaine Maxwell for a violation of parking regulations in New York City.

keyFacts: Ghislaine Maxwell was issued a parking summons for a violation on June 19, 2013.
The vehicle involved was a 2007 black Cadillac with the plate number 894NYE.
The summons was issued by the New York City Police Department, specifically from precinct 018.
